{"tid":109632,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行職員係咪睇到我資產?","createTime":"2017-02-06T05:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T17:28:15.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7930837604fd2ee0385109869c6d59d9d37a6b","tid":109632,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:54:30.000Z","msg":"咩等級既職員先睇到我資產<br />\n定係普通counter既人已經可以知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad59c3aeb38ce15b15b30b6dc282ae3544d0c10d","tid":109632,"uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"咩資產先"},{"pid":"437ae475b6336216a4f3ddac77ef1db21daba845","tid":109632,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02473598e64a9f9c7840b5ba1e5cc8c9a9c97a90","tid":109632,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩資產先</blockquote><br />\n應該只係講緊佢係銀行個幾十蚊存款"},{"pid":"f4aa32778eec7f91fe883c313c1ee76c359f9777","tid":109632,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩等級既職員先睇到我資產<br />\n定係普通counter既人已經可以知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去counter查你戶口嘢時個teller係可以睇到<br />\n但銀行職員一般唔好可以主動去查某個客戶嘅個人資料<br />\n銀行係有system check到員工有冇咁做。<br />\n<br />\ncheck到係即炒的(好似係)"},{"pid":"4ca341c27f948b2253a54bd0adec65bc95531474","tid":109632,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩資產先</blockquote><br />\n應該只係講緊佢係銀行個幾十蚊存款</blockquote><br />\n幾十蚊係唔係錢<br />\n夠膽出黎用錢掉我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3469b0fa45e32568aa10cab7501e20ca9e4342d5","tid":109632,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"如果睇唔到你啲料，銀行執得喇<br />\n擺明就係除哂你啲衫來強姦你"}]}